{
  "levelId": "block-01",
  "chapterId": "block-01",
  "worldId": "block",
  "title": "方块村门口：搭起路牌",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "village",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/block/block-01.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "穿过古树门，小小探险家来到方块村。村口的路牌倒在草地上，大家找不到地下城的方向。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是方块村门口。我们先把“搭起路牌”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我听到方块碰撞的声音，新的建造点就在前面。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先找稳固的方块，再一步一步搭出安全的路线。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "build",
          "prompt": "把路牌的方块一块块搭起来。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "放上木方块",
              "feedback": "路牌站稳了，木头闻起来香香的。"
            },
            {
              "label": "装上小灯",
              "feedback": "小灯亮起，地下城方向出现了。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，放上木方块让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "方块放稳后，藏在墙后的通道露出来了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这段通道接到村子的道路上，伙伴们就能一起通过。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这块特别的方块，它会成为下一座建筑的起点。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "‘方’是四四方方的形状，方块世界里到处都是它。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "right"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
        "characters": [
          "narrator",
          "block_builder",
          "hero"
        ],
        "props": [
          "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/props/block/block-01.webp"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/block/block-01.webp",
